pull.title: Improve COutPoint less operator
pull.body: This change prevents double scanning the transaction hash when sorting `COutPoint`. Mostly relevant when `COutPoint` is the `std::set` or `std::map` key type.

comments.body: `a` and `b` are not available at this point. You might need to use `other.data` and `data` (self context).
